When choosing a red lipstick, you should first determine whether you are the warm or the cold type. Try a simple test - look at the veins on your wrist. If they are blue, you are the cold type, if they are green, then you are the warm type. When choosing a new red lipstick, first of all, look at the classification based on the undertone. Then look at the texture in the next one.
If you are one of the women with cold undertones, then purple, plum, cherry or mauve lipsticks are suitable for you.
